short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This tool allows you to see data in your states based on ngx-base-state.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
NO REDUX DevTools for debugging application's state changes.
The extension provides power-ups for your Angular application based on ngx-base-state. Check all states of your application & states changes history using this extension.

This is an open source project. See the official repository for more details: https://github.com/Nillcon248/ngx-base-state
